room_title: Escape room "Dead Zone" by Trapped Escape Game in Pigeon Forge
room_description: It's been 197 days since the outbreak. Terror has begun to set in. You are out of food and most of your friends have been infected or disappeared. A small group of the uninfected have come together in efforts of coordinating with the very last helicopter rescue making its last fly over for survivors in 60 minutes. This is your only hope of survival.
